reviewText: I don't know what the the aim of this video was except wasting my time. It would have been better if they had left off the sound. Actually nothing could rescue this vieo. Now to the porn on the video. If you are looking for gay porn, you be better off with "Twink Cowboy". If you are looking for music, don't waste your money. This comment is for Amazon, I don't know what your policy is for selecting products to sell but this video should never have been offered for sale. I am surprised you usually have good deals but at over $22.00 this is not a good deal.
